	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=13189><span id= >Datajack</span></a><br><span id=notbold>14 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default [2.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>If you are KOS from everyone in HHK from killing the guards/nobles, you can still turn in the HK key 102 to the assistant with the hide trick. <br><br>Hit the assistant with calm/pacify to reduce agro range. then open trade window with hk 102. have someone invis or superior camo you so you disappear. then hit the trade button to hand the assistant your key. you should then be able to get the needed note. <br><br>DO NOT give the assistant the key if you're KOS con, she will eat it (much to my dismay). <br><br>Also, even being KOS to all the faction hits that HHK guard deaths gives you I was still able to hand in and get soulfire from brother hayle after doing the bandit sash quest about 40 times. <br><br>hope it helps.</p>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
